text: The Portland Trail Blazers, commonly known as the Blazers, are an American professional basketball team based in Portland, Oregon. The Trail Blazers compete in the National Basketball Association as a member of the league's Western Conference Northwest Division.
The Portland Trail Blazers have the sixth-highest all-time NBA regular season win-loss record percentage (.538) among all current NBA teams.
